Introduction

The Hotel Reviews dataset is a collection of customer reviews and feedback about various hotels, providing valuable insights into the hospitality industry. Typically sourced from online review platforms or booking websites, this dataset encompasses a diverse range of hotels worldwide. Each review entry includes details such as the hotels name, location, user ratings, and textual feedback from guests. Analyzing this dataset can offer profound insights into customer preferences, satisfaction levels, and specific aspects of hotels that influence their experiences. Researchers and businesses can leverage sentiment analysis and natural language processing techniques to extract sentiments expressed in these reviews, enabling them to understand trends, identify areas for improvement, and enhance overall customer satisfaction in the hotel industry. The Hotel Reviews dataset is a valuable resource for researchers, data scientists, and industry professionals aiming to gain a deeper understanding of customer opinions and preferences in the realm of hospitality.
